1 Dedication Account; altering a grant program for certain bus rapid transit systems
2 to require that Montgomery County, instead of other counties or municipal
3 corporations, be the grantee under the program; providing for the duration of a grant
4 agreement under a certain bus rapid transit grant program; increasing the amount
5 of an appropriation that the Governor is required to include in the annual budget
6 bill each year for the Bus Rapid Transit Fund; and generally relating to horse racing
7 in the State.
